review: I have been in consultation with Dr Mili Joshi for a variety of health issues ever since the lockdown began. Dr Joshi has been prompt, unambiguous and reassuring in her diagnosis and advice. Her quick prognosis and follow-up was crucial in my recovery from Appendicitis. More recently, she has been of invaluable support when my parents (both 80+) tested positive for Covid. Dr Joshi is empathetic, has the patience to address concerns and does not believe in prescribing medicines when avoidable. I thank Dr Joshi wholeheartedly for her continuing support.
